`frontend` (前端用户体验受影响)\n\n4. **关键指标**：\n   - `rrt_max` 表示响应时间达到峰值\n   - 调用关系 `checkoutservice->cartservice` 和 `cartservice->redis` 显示了错误传播路径\n\n建议优先检查redis集群的健康状态和资源使用情况，这很可能是系统故障的根本原因。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to severe performance degradation in redis operations (HMSET and HGET) leading to cascading failures in cartservice and checkoutservice"}
